reviewText: This video is huge eye opener. All Americans should see this video and remember to vote.

It remains difficult to understand way it is taking so long to be delivered, after all it aired on TV in June 2008. When I saw it on TV, the production cried out for everyone, in particularly taxpayers, should watch. Every tax payer in this country should get a picture of the non-ETHICAL standards of our elected congressman.

I would like to be able to review this video and I don't understand why it is taking so long to be delivered, after all it aired on TV weeks ago.  When I saw it on TV, I thought that it was a program that everyone should watch.  Every tax payer in this country should get a picture of the ETHICAL standards of our elected congressman.
